// FileUpload
// Drag-and-drop file upload zone with file type and size validation.
// Supports click-to-browse as well as drag-over, drag-leave, and drop interactions.

FUNCTION formatFileSize(bytes) -> string
  Converts a byte count to a human-readable string (B, KB, MB, GB).

---

FUNCTION validateFiles(files) -> { valid, errors }
  Checks each file against accepted types and maxSize constraints.
  Returns a list of valid files and an array of error messages for rejected files.

---

FUNCTION handleFiles(files)
  Calls validateFiles on the file list.
  Updates error state with any validation failures.
  Calls onChange with the valid files.

---

FUNCTION handleDrop(e)
  Prevents default browser drop behavior.
  Clears drag-over state.
  Extracts dropped files and calls handleFiles.

---

FUNCTION handleDragOver(e)
  Prevents default to allow drop.
  Sets drag-over visual state.

---

FUNCTION handleDragLeave(e)
  Clears drag-over visual state.

---

FUNCTION handleInputChange(e)
  Extracts files from the file input element and calls handleFiles.

---

FUNCTION handleClick()
  Programmatically clicks the hidden file input to open the browser file picker.

---

FUNCTION FileUpload(props) -> ReactNode                                   EXPORT
  Renders a bordered drop zone with drag-over highlight.
  Contains a hidden file input and forwards clicks to it via handleClick.
  Shows accepted file types, max size, and any validation errors below the zone.
  Lists selected files with their names and sizes.
